<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>Flight Ticket</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 18mm;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background: #fff;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
        }

        .letterpad-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 14px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .letterpad-title {
            font-size: 22pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .letterpad-subtitle {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 2px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .letterpad-contact {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .letterpad-contact span {
            margin: 0 12px;
        }

        .letterpad-gst {
            font-size: 8.5pt;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 4px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        .ticket-header {
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .ticket-header-left {
            float: left;
            font-size: 18pt;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .ticket-header-right {
            float: right;
            font-size: 10pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .ticket-header-right strong {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .clearfix {
            clear: both;
        }

        .route-strip {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .route-cities {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            float: left;
        }

        .route-cities .arrow {
            color: #adb5bd;
            margin: 0 6px;
        }

        .route-date-main {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            float: right;
        }

        .segment-card {
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-top: none;
            background: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .segment-header {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .segment-header-left {
            float: left;
        }

        .segment-header-right {
            float: right;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .segment-label {
            font-size: 8pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .segment-number {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        .airline-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .flight-number {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .timeline-body {
            padding: 16px 18px;
        }

        .time-block {
            width: 32%;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 6px;
        }

        .time-block.departure {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .time-block.arrival {
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 0;
        }

        .time-code {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .time-value {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .time-date {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .time-airport {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #495057;
            margin-top: 4px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .time-airport strong {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .duration-connector {
            width: 30%;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 8px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .duration-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: #ced4da;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .duration-text {
            font-size: 10pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .duration-class {
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .plane-icon {
            font-size: 12pt;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .info-bar {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .info-bar-left {
            float: left;
        }

        .info-bar-right {
            float: right;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .layover-strip {
            background: #fff8e1;
            border-left: 3px solid #ffc107;
            border-right: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ced4da;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #856404;
        }

        .layover-text {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .layover-details {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #a08030;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        .travellers-section {
            margin-top: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
        }

        .section-title-bar {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .travellers-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .travellers-table thead th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 8.5pt;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .travellers-table tbody td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .travellers-table tbody tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .traveller-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .traveller-passport {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .pnr-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            background: #f1f3f5;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .ticket-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .notes-section {
            margin-top: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
        }

        .notes-content {
            padding: 12px 18px;
            background: #fafbfc;
        }

        .notes-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .notes-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #495057;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .notes-list li::before {
            content: '\2022';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }

        .notes-list li strong {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .footer-bar {
            margin-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ced4da;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .footer-left {
            float: left;
            max-width: 60%;
        }

        .footer-right {
            float: right;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .footer-gst {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .page-wrapper {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 10mm;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-wrapper">

    <!-- LETTERPAD HEADER -->
    <div class="letterpad-header">
        <div class="letterpad-title">Friendly Wings Travel</div>
        <div class="letterpad-subtitle">International &amp; Domestic Flight Bookings</div>
        <div class="letterpad-contact">
            <span>&#9993; thamizh@friendlywings.com</span>
            <span>&#9742; 8098597634, 9488493370</span>
        </div>
        <div class="letterpad-gst">GSTIN: 33BVWPT7026F1Z3</div>
    </div>

    <!-- TICKET HEADER -->
    <div class="ticket-header">
        <div class="ticket-header-left">E-Ticket</div>
        <div class="ticket-header-right">
            Trip ID: <strong>$!tripId</strong>
            #if($travelDate && $travelDate != "")
            &nbsp;|&nbsp; Travel Date: $travelDate
            #end
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ROUTE STRIP -->
    <div class="route-strip">
        <div class="route-cities">
            $!route
        </div>
        <div class="route-date-main">
            $!travelDate
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SEGMENTS -->
    #foreach($seg in $segments)
    <div class="segment-card">
        <div class="segment-header">
            <div class="segment-header-left">
                <span class="segment-number">$foreach.count</span>
                <span class="segment-label">
                    #if($foreach.count == 1)
                        Outbound Flight
                    #elseif($foreach.count == $segments.size())
                        Connecting Flight
                    #else
                        Connecting Flight
                    #end
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="segment-header-right">
                <div class="airline-name">$!seg.airline</div>
                <div class="flight-number">Flight $!seg.flightNumber
                    #if($seg.fareType && $seg.fareType != "") &middot; $seg.fareType #end
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-body">
            <div class="time-block departure">
                <div class="time-code">$!seg.departureAirportCode</div>
                <div class="time-value">$!seg.departureTime</div>
                <div class="time-date">$!seg.departureDate</div>
                <div class="time-airport">
                    <strong>$!seg.departureAirportName</strong><br />
                    #if($seg.departureTerminal && $seg.departureTerminal != "")
                    Terminal $seg.departureTerminal
                    #end
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="duration-connector">
                <div class="plane-icon">&#9992;</div>
                <div class="duration-line"></div>
                <div class="duration-text">$!seg.duration</div>
                <div class="duration-class">$!seg.travelClass</div>
            </div>

            <div class="time-block arrival">
                <div class="time-code">$!seg.arrivalAirportCode</div>
                <div class="time-value">$!seg.arrivalTime</div>
                <div class="time-date">$!seg.arrivalDate</div>
                <div class="time-airport">
                    <strong>$!seg.arrivalAirportName</strong><br />
                    #if($seg.arrivalTerminal && $seg.arrivalTerminal != "")
                    Terminal $seg.arrivalTerminal
                    #end
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-bar">
            <div class="info-bar-left">
                <span class="info-label">Baggage:</span> $!seg.baggage
            </div>
            <div class="info-bar-right">
                #if($seg.operatedBy && $seg.operatedBy != "")
                <span class="info-label">Operated By:</span> $seg.operatedBy
                #end
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- LAYOVER (if not last segment) -->
    #if($seg.layover && $seg.layover != "" && $foreach.count < $segments.size())
    <div class="layover-strip">
        <span class="layover-text">Layover</span>
        <span class="layover-details">$seg.layover</span>
    </div>
    #end
    #end

    <!-- TRAVELLERS -->
    #if($travellers && $travellers.size() > 0)
    <div class="travellers-section">
        <div class="section-title-bar">Passenger Details</div>
        <table class="travellers-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width:40%">Passenger Name</th>
                    <th style="width:25%">Passport</th>
                    <th style="width:20%">Airline PNR</th>
                    <th style="width:15%">Ticket No.</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                #foreach($traveller in $travellers)
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="traveller-name">$!traveller.name</div>
                        <div class="traveller-passport">Adult</div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        #if($traveller.passportNumber && $traveller.passportNumber != "")
                        <span class="ticket-code">$traveller.passportNumber</span>
                        #else
                        <span class="ticket-code">-</span>
                        #end
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        #if($traveller.pnr && $traveller.pnr != "")
                        <span class="pnr-code">$traveller.pnr</span>
                        #else
                        <span class="pnr-code">-</span>
                        #end
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        #if($traveller.ticketNumber && $traveller.ticketNumber != "")
                        <span class="ticket-code">$traveller.ticketNumber</span>
                        #else
                        <span class="ticket-code">-</span>
                        #end
                    </td>
                </tr>
                #end
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    #end

    <!-- NOTES -->
    <div class="notes-section">
        <div class="section-title-bar">Important Travel Information</div>
        <div class="notes-content">
            <ul class="notes-list">
                <li><strong>Check-in:</strong> Please arrive at the airport at least <strong>4 hours</strong> before international departure. Check-in counters close 90 minutes prior to departure.</li>
                <li><strong>Identification:</strong> Carry a valid photo ID and passport (minimum 6 months validity) for check-in and immigration.</li>
                <li><strong>Visa &amp; Immigration:</strong> Ensure you hold valid visas and immigration clearances for all transit and destination countries.</li>
                <li><strong>Electronics:</strong> Devices larger than a smartphone must be checked in (except medical devices). Power banks must be carried in hand baggage.</li>
                <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Use your Trip ID <strong>$!tripId</strong> for all booking-related communication.</li>
                <li><strong>Seat Selection:</strong> Pre-select seats via the airline website using your PNR code to avoid last-minute charges.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="footer-bar">
        <div class="footer-left">
            This is a computer-generated e-ticket and does not require a signature.<br />
            For any assistance, contact us at thamizh@friendlywings.com or call 8098597634, 9488493370
        </div>
        <div class="footer-right">
            <div class="footer-gst">GSTIN: 33BVWPT7026F1Z3</div>
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
